%e A142961 k=3: Sigma(3, n) = Sum_{p=0..n} p^3 * binomial(2*p, p) * binomial(2*(n-p), n-p) = (4*n/16)*n^2*(3 + 5*n), for n >= 0. This is the sequence {0, 2, 52, 648, 5888, 44800, 304128, 1906688, 11272192, 63700992, ...}.
